WEBVTT

00:00.823 --> 00:03.273
What's this about?
Family members are missing.

00:03.298 --> 00:05.015
Police think it's an
extortion racket.

00:05.040 --> 00:06.159
Is it my mother's?

00:06.184 --> 00:09.085
You trusted them?! I wanted to know
if Mama is still alive.

00:09.110 --> 00:10.550
There is no-one you can trust!

00:10.575 --> 00:11.775
I know what you are.

00:11.800 --> 00:13.360
I know what you did with the van.

00:13.400 --> 00:15.600
Where can you go where
you'll be safe?

00:15.640 --> 00:18.040
I'm not buying her. I'm taking her.

00:18.080 --> 00:19.959
You come near me again,
I'll kill you!

00:19.960 --> 00:22.919
Murder weapon? No obvious wood
splinter. A metal bar?

00:22.920 --> 00:24.120
Metal bar would do it.

00:24.160 --> 00:26.017
Wear this. You'll be safer.

00:27.800 --> 00:30.400
A267. B means "Back to London".

00:30.440 --> 00:32.240
94 kilometres to Charing Cross.

00:32.280 --> 00:34.360
It's not a password. It's a place.

00:36.560 --> 00:44.000
This programme contains scenes which
some viewers may find upsetting from the start

00:46.280 --> 00:53.679
♪ Costestes e spiritu

00:53.680 --> 01:01.360
♪ Silentium. ♪

01:03.000 --> 01:09.074
